abstract: >-
  Forever — a TypeScript agent framework I built because I kept rebuilding the same pieces for different projects. 16+ LLM adapters, RAG, MCP, a workflow graph, the usual suspects. The name is half joke, half ambition; the codebase is more honest than the name.
